data.description:
Beautiful house in a well desired Lost Creek neighborhood in Eanes ISD.
Highly updated house with Marble and wood flooring, brand new carpet, granite kitchen, views from front and back. New windows and whole house blinds. Almost quarter acre land. Easy access to 360. Please contact Neil @ 512-466-6308 if interested.
data.whatILove: Gorgeous house in the heart of westlake in the most desirable subdivision of Lost Creek. Beautiful 2 Story home with Marble floor in the Foyer and Family room, Brand new Wooden floors and Carpet in the bedroom. Brand new windows &  blinds on all windows. 3 specious bedrooms with 3 full baths. Spectacular view from the front of the house and nicely wooded backyard with lots of trees. Exemplary EANES ISD Schools and very accessible to Mopac, 360 and I-35.
